beer.beer_description: Brilliant copper color with a lingering, lacy white head. The nose sings of grapefruit, pine needles, citron, roses and bergamot. The flavor is rich in the citrusy, resiny flavors from Columbus and Cascade hops packed into this beer balanced artfully with a solid malt character and crisp bitterness leading to a beautifully dry, light herbal finish.
